description: Erection of part 5, part 6 and part 7 storey buildings to provide 1100 sqm of class B1 (Commercial) 192 sqm of Class A1 (retail) floor space and 106 residential units, comprising 37x1 bed; 40x2 bed; 17x3 bed; 11x4 bed and 1x5 bed flats together with 21 car parking spaces.  Demolition of existing buildings.
